{"tid":733890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍艦航經台灣海峽      中國國台辦:兩岸應共同反對","createTime":"2018-07-08T07:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T12:38:16.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"35284e86bf430b6cf574424fc8e3472b8e270b7f","tid":733890,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T07:26:32.000Z","msg":"美軍艦航經台灣海峽 國台辦:兩岸應共同反對<br />\n<br />\n2018/07/08 14:22<br />\n<br />\n美軍太平洋艦隊證實兩艘海軍軍艦昨日航經台灣海峽。對此，中國大陸國台辦<br />\n主任劉結一今日表示美國此行為應該被兩岸民眾共同譴責反對，還要台灣民眾<br />\n不要去幫美國打台灣牌。<br />\n<br />\n中央社報導，中國大陸國務院台灣事務辦公室主任劉結一今天在海峽兩岸青年<br />\n發展論壇上向媒體表示，堅決反對任何危害中方「國家利益」的事情，「這是<br />\n我們不能夠接受的」。一段時間以來，美國一直在打台灣牌，打台灣牌的目的<br />\n是非常明確的。<br />\n<br />\n劉結一說，美國這種作法，傷害台灣民眾利益、傷害全體中國人民利益，也應<br />\n該受到兩岸民眾共同反對。台灣民眾應該認清美國這些行動的真實目的，千萬<br />\n不要有人去幫助美國打台灣牌，傷害兩岸民眾與台灣民眾利益。<br />\n（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180708/1387410/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180708%2F1387410%2F&d=%2BDHbO%2FzWHDxt69RyF4bxTC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=86e2857d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180708%2F1387410%2F&h=ea6f2a22\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180708/1387410/</a>"},{"pid":"8229f9393de5b96ba802a49513290c2a72e4d4b0","tid":733890,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T07:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f12d393f7622a86c522b9e0cf6d138433778367","tid":733890,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T07:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RZc7r5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRZc7r5a.jpg&h=bb712195&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4989763b110849306501825757d25f38e47bb9b6","tid":733890,"uid":159674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T07:31:00.000Z","msg":"反佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbaa7f9d4e2a12242a687480825a0e058774c50","tid":733890,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T12:38:16.000Z","msg":"哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}